top_stories.title: OpenAI releases o3-pro, a souped-up version of its o3 AI reasoning model
top_stories.description: OpenAI has launched o3-pro, an AI model that the company claims is its most capable yet.
top_stories.author: Kyle Wiggers

top_stories.title: Google rolls out Android 16 to Pixel phones, unveils AI-powered edit suggestion for Google Photos
top_stories.description: Google is releasing Android 16 to Pixel phones and rolling out additional updates to other Pixel devices.
top_stories.author: Ivan Mehta

top_stories.title: Applications of Density Estimation to Legal Theory
top_stories.description:
A brief analysis using density estimation to compare the two-verdict and three-verdict systems.
The post Applications of Density Estimation to Legal Theory appeared first on Towards Data Science.
top_stories.author: Jimin Kang

top_stories.title: Apple’s upgraded AI models underwhelm on performance
top_stories.description: Apple has announced updates to the AI models that power its suite of Apple Intelligence features across iOS, macOS, and more. But according to the company's own benchmarks, the models underperform older models from rival tech firms including OpenAI.
top_stories.author: Kyle Wiggers

top_stories.title: Enterprise AI startup Glean lands a $7.2B valuation
top_stories.description: Glean announced on Tuesday that is raised a $150 million Series F led by Wellington Management at a $7.2 billion valuation.
top_stories.author: Julie Bort
